I recently solved this issue myself, for anyone else struggling with this error, here's how I solved it:
in your functions.php, index.php and page.php files, change the way you're enclosing your conditionals, from this:

if (have_posts());
    while (have_posts()) : 
        the_content();
    endwhile;
endif;

to this:

if (have_posts()){
    while (have_posts()) : 
        the_content();
    endwhile;
}

After that, you should see the error disappearing and you'll be able to work with your template.

